snippet.title: Diana and the Magic Flower. Learn to understand your desires and value friendship | Moral stories
snippet.description:
Diana finds a magic flower. Each petal can fulfill any wish of the girl. Diana wants new toys and things that Roma does not allow her. But, having reached the last petal, the girl understands that it is better to learn how to be friends! A moral story for children about the value of friendship.
Thanks for watching!
